OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Author Chimamanda Ngozi Adichie has    
OL,6, said she worries society is suffering  
OL,7, from an "epidemic of self-censorship". 
OL,9,FIn a BBC lecture on freedom of speech, 
OL,10,Fthe writer said young people were      
OL,11,Fgrowing up "afraid to ask questions for
OL,12,Ffear of asking the wrong questions".   
OL,14,FSuch a climate could lead to "the death
OL,15,Fof curiosity, the death of learning and
OL,16,Fthe death of creativity", the          
OL,17,Faward-winning Nigerian author warned.  
OL,19,F"No human endeavour requires freedom as
OL,20,Fmuch as creativity does," she added.   
